<directions xmlns:php="http://php.net/xsl">
<step><![CDATA[1. Crack egg in a bowl, add soy sauce,,stir and mix well(make sure egg white and egg yolk mix evenly).]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[2. Clean leek, drain well, chop]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[3. Heat oil in a wok over high heat,slip egg liquid,change heat to low. Sway egg making the liquid spread on the bottom of the wok evenly.Stir into blocks when the liquid becomes solid.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[4. Add five species powder,the rest salt, leek section,stir fry 2mins,or until leek becomes soft.]]></step>
<step><![CDATA[5. Turn off heat,arrange in a plate,serve.]]></step>
&gt;</directions>
